• Tide Naturals delivers a strong product cleaning and whitening performance via a dual surfactant system and brightener technology.

• Tide Naturals contains a surfactant derived from natural palm and coconut oil as well as several natural oils, to provide the natural-like freshness or fragrance of lemon and sandalwood.

• Tide Naturals uses water-soluble sodium sulphate that helps provide the additional benefit of keeping your hands soft.
